### Get All Routes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/routes

### Get Route by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/routes/1

### Create Route
POST http://localhost:3000/api/routes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Metro Route 2",
  "code": "MET001",
  "stops": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "order": 1,
      "eta": 10
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "order": 2,
      "eta": 20
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "order": 2,
      "eta": 20
    }
  ]
}

### Update Route
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/routes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Downtown Route Updated",
  "code": "DT001-UPDATED"
}

### Delete Route
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/routes/1

### Create Trip with Trip Stops (based on route)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "routeId": 1,
  "driverId": 1,
  "vehicleId": 1
}

### Get Trip by ID (includes trip stops)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trips/1

### Get Trip Stops
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trips/1/stops

### End Trip (triggers metrics calculation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trips/1/end
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endLocation": 5
}
